name: Bujinki Ahashima
desc:
2 monsters with the same Level
Cannot be used as Link Material. If this card is Link Summoned: You can Special Summon 2 monsters with the same Level (1 from your hand and 1 from your GY), but negate their effects (if any), and if you do, immediately after this effect resolves, Xyz Summon 1 Xyz Monster using only those 2 monsters. If an Xyz Monster this card points to detaches its material(s) to activate an effect (except during the Damage Step): You can target 1 Spell/Trap your opponent controls; destroy it. You can only use each effect of "Bujinki Ahashima" once per turn.
